'''Dave Gibbons''' provided the cover art and all illustrations for the ''[[Vader's Quest]]'' series of comics as well as [[Chewbacca (2000) 2|''Chewbacca'' (2000) 2]]. He also provided artwork for [[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine|''Star Wars Galaxy'' magazine]]. He is most well known for having illustrated [[Wikipedia:Watchmen|''Watchmen'']] (written by [[Alan Moore]]).{{Mediacat|imagecat=Images by Dave Gibbons}}

